                                                                                            <p class="word-copy-lh-mb"><a href="https://religion.lafayette.edu/people/eric-ziolkowski/"><strong>Eric Ziolkowski</strong></a> is Helen H.P. Manson Professor Emeritus at Lafayette College, Easton, Pennsylvania. He is author of numerous books, articles, and essays in the comparative study of religion and literature; served 2002–12 as North American senior editor of the journal <em>Literature and Theology</em> (Oxford); 2004–24 as a main editor of the <em>Encyclopedia of the Bible and Its Reception</em> (De Gruyter), volumes 1–24; and co-edits the series Studies in Religion and the Arts (Brill).</p>
